4Geeks Academy offers a course called "Become a AI Machine Learning Engineer" that aims to start a career in data science and build ML models. The course has a duration of 16 weeks, with 3 classes weekly and a maximum of 12 people per class. No previous experience is required. The instructors, Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena, have extensive experience and expertise in the field of AI and machine learning. The course covers topics like Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, statistics, and various ML algorithms. Students will also learn to develop their own AI projects, from development to deployment and maintenance. The course offers recognized certificates and is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit their website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop